    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "8. Expenditure of Ministries in charge of social sectors, as recommended by the World Bank in the absence of a budgetary functional classification. An adjustor will be defined in case of expenditure cuts, which will ensure an increase of the share of poverty-reducing socia spending in the total of primary current expenditure (see TMU for details). ",
        "page_idx": 48
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "9/10. DAO is defined as all expenditures which do not go through the standard spending procedure. Regularization of DAO consists in recording the expenditure in the correspondent line of the budget. This will be done within 45 days after the end of the quarter. ",
        "page_idx": 48
    },
    {
